cts dust-sensitive Balmer decrements,\nspectroscopic stellar metallicities, PAH mass fractions, and the age- and\nmetallicity-sensitive features D$_{\\mathrm{n}}$4000 and H$\\delta$. Although the\nmodel passes all these tests, we caution that we have not yet assessed its\nperformance at higher redshift or the accuracy of recovered stellar masses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2016 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Apr 2017 20:43:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-14"}
