 geometry for the dense CSM.\nBased on our X-ray spectral analyses, we estimate the radius of the torus-like\nCSM to be on the order of ~5 times 10^{16} cm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2016 20:00:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-14"}
