lence classes is at most $2^{2^t}$, improving on\nearlier bounds of the form $(t+1)^{2^t}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2016 11:50:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-30"}
